    ns1:otherInformation """All the additional documentation to follow this course will be available at the Moodle platform of the course.
In case there is a forced confinement situation due to COVID-19, all the lectures will be available in video files. The exams will be carried out using the Moodle platform of the course."""@es ;
    ns1:periodEndingMonth "Junio"@es ;
    ns1:periodStartingMonth "Febrero"@es ;
