    schema:description "The main objective of the course is for the students to achieve a basic knowledge on different technological processes that are applied to materials used mainly in the nano and microelectronic fields. Furthermore, the course will also analyze the main effects that those technological processes have on the optical and electrical properties of different optoelectronic devices."@es ;
